lead_paragraph: The United States Mail Steamer Illinois, Lieut. H. J. HARTSTEINE, arrived at this port Saturday morning at about two o'clock, having left Chagres on the 9th inst. She touched at Norfolk, Va., from which place the leading items of her news have been already telegraphed.

headline.main: TWO WEEKS LATER FROM CALIFORNIA.; ARRIVAL OF THE STEAMER ILLINOIS. LATER FROM OREGON.
